CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper August 13, 1955, pg. 30, reads: "Part of the Wallace Family - Catherine Wallace, the little girl with the big voice, is one of a family of ten children. Her father is dead. Part of the family is pictured above. Left to right: Idella, sister; Danny, brother; Catherine; Mrs. Idella Wallace, mother, and Rachel, sister. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Idella Wallace, Danny Wallace, singer Catherine Wallace, mother Idella Wallace, and Rachel Wallace posed in living room
